OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA dry, warm
OL,6,Fand bright evening with hazy sunny
OL,7,Fperiods. It will then remain dry for
OL,8,Fthe rest of the night with clear
OL,9,Fspells and light winds.
OL,10,
OL,11,CWednesday:FDry with early morning
OL,12,Fcloud soon burning off to leave a warm
OL,13,Fday with sunny spells. Feeling fresher
OL,14,Fon the east coast with the risk of
OL,15,Fpatchy low cloud.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
